01:20:34,320 --> 01:20:38,015
Cekaj. Albert,
Willy pidzama je.

951
01:20:38,632 --> 01:20:40,647
U redu..
Aha..

952
01:20:45,798 --> 01:20:50,910
Tata. Tata.

953
01:20:52,627 --> 01:20:54,489
Tata.

954
01:21:02,520 --> 01:21:04,612
Tata?

955
01:21:08,615 --> 01:21:10,784
Majko!

956
01:21:12,723 --> 01:21:15,382
Majko!
-Sta je?

957
01:21:20,767 --> 01:21:23,600
Richard!

958
01:21:59,165 --> 01:22:01,759
Kako to mislis,
pratio te je?

959
01:22:01,794 --> 01:22:05,569
Bije bitno.
-Za mene jeste!

960
01:22:05,604 --> 01:22:07,429
Kako se zove?

961
01:22:07,464 --> 01:22:09,273
Will Donner.

962
01:22:42,542 --> 01:22:43,862
Izvinite.

963
01:22:43,863 --> 01:22:47,238
Vi ste bili u timu za naucne radove
u prvom razredu srednje?

964
01:22:47,273 --> 01:22:50,679
I vi ste bili, zar ne?
-Tako je.

965
01:22:54,490 --> 01:22:58,310
Hvala sto si pristao da se vidimo.
-Svakako.

966
01:22:58,345 --> 01:23:00,453
Proslo je toliko dugo.

967
01:23:01,483 --> 01:23:03,427
Vidi, ja...

968
01:23:06,920 --> 01:23:10,235
Joey, mislim da
sam malo zabrljala.

969
01:23:10,270 --> 01:23:14,197
Ja sam cuo da
si imala tesku godinu.

970
01:23:14,232 --> 01:23:16,732
Od koga si cuo?

971
01:23:18,016 --> 01:23:22,083
Od Willy-ja.
Willy-ja, da.

972
01:23:22,586 --> 01:23:24,745
Zato sam te
pozvala.

973
01:23:24,780 --> 01:23:29,840
Osecam se strasno u
vezi svega sto se dogodilo.

974
01:23:29,875 --> 01:23:31,622
Znam da je bio kod tebe,

975
01:23:31,657 --> 01:23:34,217
pa sam pomislila
da ste u kontaktu.

976
01:23:34,341 --> 01:23:36,267
Nisam ni znala
da mu se svidjam.

977
01:23:36,302 --> 01:23:40,324
Da mu se svidjas?
Ti se nalazis u njegovoj aorti.

978
01:23:40,359 --> 01:23:42,779
Sta?
Nista..

979
01:23:42,814 --> 01:23:44,967
On tako kaze.

980
01:23:47,175 --> 01:23:51,661
Ako razgovarase sa njim,
samo mu reci koliko mi je zao?

981
01:23:53,277 --> 01:23:54,914
U redu.

982
01:24:18,158 --> 01:24:19,918
Zdravo, Jim.

983
01:24:24,562 --> 01:24:28,577
Willy ti je poslao ovo.
On je u San Franciscu.

984
01:24:28,612 --> 01:24:31,075
On se uvodi
u Fisherman's Wharf.

985
01:24:31,110 --> 01:24:34,113
On je poslao jos jedno pismo
za mene.

986
01:24:34,614 --> 01:24:37,538
Nije znao gde da ga posalje
nakon sto ti je otac umro.

987
01:24:38,016 --> 01:24:40,340
Izvoli.
-Hvala.

988
01:24:44,706 --> 01:24:47,620
-Kako ti je majka?
Dobro je.

989
01:24:47,655 --> 01:24:49,289
Jeste?
-Da.

990
01:24:49,324 --> 01:24:52,527
Lepo...

991
01:24:54,447 --> 01:24:56,400
Hvala ti.

992
01:25:16,431 --> 01:25:18,488
Draga Emma,

993
01:25:18,523 --> 01:25:21,414
Te dve reci,
"Draga Emma"

994
01:25:21,449 --> 01:25:25,020
Vode me do onog vremena
kada smo pisali pisma,

995
01:25:25,055 --> 01:25:26,977
Nakon sto su
mi roditelji poginuli.

996
01:25:27,012 --> 01:25:30,182
Ja sam tebi pisao o mom zivotu
i novim prijateljima.

997
01:25:30,217 --> 01:25:34,379
A ti meni kako moji roditelji
uzivaju u raju.

998
01:25:34,576 --> 01:25:36,140
Istina je nista.

999
01:25:36,175 --> 01:25:39,218
Moras verovati da
bi sve bilo istina.

1000
01:25:39,929 --> 01:25:44,475
I ja sam verovao da
cemo biti zajedno zauvek.

1001
01:25:44,510 --> 01:25:46,352
Zauvek.

1002
01:25:46,857 --> 01:25:49,280
Razlog sto ti pisem
posle tolikog vremena,

1003
01:25:49,315 --> 01:25:52,142
je da sam napokon shvatio
da sam bio budala.

1004
01:25:52,177 --> 01:25:55,659
Ceo sam zivot
pravio budalu od sebe.

1005
01:25:57,076 --> 01:25:59,821
Svako pismo koje
sam napisao bilo je ljubavno.

1006
01:25:59,856 --> 01:26:03,092
Ne moze biti drugo?

1007
01:26:03,127 --> 01:26:08,238
Sada mogu videti da su sva,
osim ovoga bila losa pisma.

1008
01:26:08,781 --> 01:26:11,702
Losa ljubavna pisma
vracaju ljubav.

1009
01:26:11,737 --> 01:26:14,026
Dobra ljubavna pisma,
pisu se niza sta.

1010
01:26:14,061 --> 01:26:16,603
Ovo je konacno..

1011
01:26:16,638 --> 01:26:19,539
prvo ljubavno pismo
napisano za tebe.

1012
01:26:19,574 --> 01:26:22,272
Jer ne mogu vise
nista da ucinim za tebe.

1013
01:26:22,307 --> 01:26:24,640
Ti si vec sve ucinila.

1014
01:26:24,869 --> 01:26:28,783
Sada imam uspomene
koje ce trajati zauvek.

1015
01:26:28,818 --> 01:26:30,936
Molim te, nemoj
brinuti za mene.

1016
01:26:30,971 --> 01:26:35,944
Ja sam  "Sasvim savrsen"
Stvarno jesam. Imam sve.

1017
01:26:35,979 --> 01:26:38,518
Ako bih pozeleo jednu zelju,
ona bi bila..

1018
01:26:38,553 --> 01:26:41,945
Da samo osetis ukus ljubavi,
koju si mi donela

1019
01:26:41,980 --> 01:26:44,910
Da osetis
kako je kad se voli.

1020
01:26:45,492 --> 01:26:49,088
Tvoj prijatelj zauvek.
Will.

1021
01:26:55,581 --> 01:26:57,190
Izgubila
si se?

1022
01:26:57,225 --> 01:26:59,602
Ne, ja samo
trazim prijatelja.

1023
01:27:00,187 --> 01:27:04,801
On zonglira,
nosi pizamu.

1024
01:27:05,078 --> 01:27:07,081
White boy u pidzami?

1025
01:27:08,333 --> 01:27:12,307
To je on! Da,to je on!

1026
01:27:12,342 --> 01:27:14,903
On je tu,
blizu marketa.

1027
01:27:14,938 --> 01:27:17,103
Bice tamo sve do noci.

1028
01:27:17,138 --> 01:27:19,304
Hvala Vam.

1029
01:27:19,339 --> 01:27:20,977
Nista, nista.

1030
01:27:21,012 --> 01:27:22,611
Hvala Vam.

1031
01:29:59,426 --> 01:30:01,907
Da li me ti
pratis?

